.\" Manpage for mde.
.\" Contact gwenole.capp@gmail.com to correct errors or typos.
.TH man 7 "12 Apr 2020" "1.0" "mde man page"
.SH NAME
mde \- create a Multidimensional Data Entity
.SH SYNOPSIS
.mde cp
[\fI\,OPTION\/\fR]... [\fI\,-T\/\fR] \fI\,SOURCE DEST\/\fR
.SH DESCRIPTION

.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-v\fR, \fB\-\-version\fR
get version
.TP
\fB\-e, \fB\-\-nomenu
GL display only, use all default or runtime arguments
.TP
\fB\-g, \fB\-\-glmode
for graphic display mode
.TP
\fB\-f, \fB\-\-file filename
for loading a file before start
.TP
\fB\-n, \fB\-\-font font
set the font
.TP
\fB\-s, \fB\-\-font-size size
set the font size
.TP
\fB\-o, \fB\-\-font-color r,g,b,a
set color and alpha for the font
.TP
\fB\-b, \fB\-\-box
display a frame box for each text
.TP
\fB\-c, \fB\-\-box-color r,g,b,a
set text box color with RGBA
.TP
\fB\-p, \fB\-\-padding x,y
to set the padding with floats x and y
.TP
\fB\-a, \fB\-\-origin x,y,z
to set the coordinates of origin
.TP
\fB\-r, \fB\-\-offset-rule
to set the offset rules
.TP
\fB\-m, \fB\-\-move
for moving mode (makes the MDE move and all axis)
.TP
\fB\-d, \fB\-\-background-color r,g,b,a
to set background color with RGBA
.SH BUGS
No known bugs.
.SH AUTHOR
Written by Gwenole Capp.
